review_text: WHEN WAS THE NAME CHANGED? THIS USE TO BE CALLED " THE WOMANS JUSTICE CENTER "

name: SAFE Family Justice Centers- Riverside Location
review_text:
So, my ex husband is abusive and harassing me even though he has a restraining order against me (long story but this instance it was completely inappropriate, he put hands on me first.) and my social worker advised me to come to this place to get a RO against him.

I get there, tell her the story, and because he was the first to talk to the cops, they refused to give me any assistance. Only general advice. The situation is actually very common where the actual victim is the one who's made to look like the perpetrator, because the abusers know we protect them and use the legal system to further abuse us.

It's grimey bc this place is aware of the issue but refuse to help anyone listed as a defendant. If we already know better, we should do better.
